### Get all users (no filters)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/getAllUsers

###

### Get all users with empty queries
GET http://localhost:3000/api/getAllUsers?queries=[]

###

### Get all users with search
GET http://localhost:3000/api/getAllUsers?search=john

###

### Get all users with search and empty queries
GET http://localhost:3000/api/getAllUsers?queries=[]&search=john

###

# Note: Complex queries (like Query.limit()) need to be handled in backend
# The queries parameter currently expects array format but Appwrite Query objects
# are better constructed server-side

###

